data.description: This home is located in a family friendly neighborhood conveniently located minutes from shopping, dining and Huber schools. This beautiful one level brick home is furnished with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a family room with eat in breakfast bar and spacious living room. There is a 2 car attached garage with a fenced in back yard and covered patio. The new roof and furnace was installed in 2021.
